---
title: Indo-Chinese Style Chilli Paneer with Stir-Fried Veg and Basmati Rice
description: Our Indo Chinese Style Chilli Paneer is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/indo-chinese-style-chilli-paneer-a7708051-5f8bf208.jpg
